te>Liahona</cite>, mayo de 2018, pág. 90.</p></li><li data-marker=15. id=note15><p data-aid=140059895 id=note15_p1>Conversación personal.</p></li><li data-marker=16. id=note16><p data-aid=140059900 id=note16_p1>Dale G. Renlund, “<a class=cross-ref data-old-href=../../../general-conference/2018/10/choose-you-this-day.html href="/general-conference/2018/10/choose-you-this-day?lang=spa">Escogeos hoy</a>”, <cite>Liahona</cite>, noviembre de 2018, pág. 106.</p></li><li data-marker=17. id=note17><p data-aid=140059905 id=note17_p1><a class=scripture-ref data-old-href="../../../scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.html?verse=18-19#p18" href="/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.18-19?lang=spa#p18">Doctrina y Convenios 19:18–19</a>.</p></li></ol></footer></div></article><div class=startHandle-2o_6p touch-action=none></div><div class=endHandle-wg4Dv touch-action=none></div></div><div class="callout-EaEKb hidden-6EhVw sc-bZQynM dDOxTx" style=bottom:NaNpx><div class="sc-htoDjs fHktW"><div class="sc-gzVnrw kPxdrJ"></div><div class=signIn-215_y></div></div></div></section></section><div class=mobileNav-1qobD><a class="mobileIcon-3ABLr mobilePrev-1Jf8d" href=/study/liahona/2019/05/14uchtdorf><button dir=ltr class="iconButton--V5Iv navButton-WGhZC"><svg style=width:1em;height:1em viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns=http://www.w3.org/2000/svg role=presentation> <path fill=currentColor d="M4.438 10.856a.77.77 0 0 1 .097-.117l6.709-6.71a.755.755 0 0 1 1.065-.003.751.751 0 0 1-.005 1.064L6.6 10.795h11.647c.403 0 .744.335.744.75 0 .417-.333.75-.744.75H6.565l5.74 5.739a.755.755 0 0 1 .004 1.065.751.751 0 0 1-1.065-.005l-6.71-6.709a.757.757 0 0 1-.127-.169.755.755 0 0 1-.416-.671c0-.31.184-.574.447-.689z"> </path></svg></button></a><a class="mobileIcon-3ABLr mobileNext-1J33m" href=/study/liahona/2019/05/16eyring><button style=transform:scale(-1) class="iconButton--V5Iv navButton-WGhZC"><svg style=width:1em;height:1em viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns=http://www.w3.org/2000/svg role=presentation> <path fill=currentColor